rmer%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AIADMK%20supremo%20J%20Jayalalithaa%2C%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20backing%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Central%20government%20was%2C%20perhaps%2C%20the%20key%20reason%20why%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Edappadi%20Palaniswamy%20(EPS)%20managed%20to%20take%20over%20and%20keep%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20is%20the%20undisputed%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20party%2C%20but%20he%20had%20to%20fight%20first%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20O.Paneerselvam%20and%20then%20Jayalalithaa's%20former%20aide%20Sasikala%20Natrajan%2C%20who%2C%20ironically%2C%20helped%20appoint%20EPS%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20the%20support%20of%20the%20BJP%20was%20useful%20in%20holding%20on%20to%20power%2C%20it%20was%20a%20futile%20alliance%20when%20it%20came%20to%20electoral%20realities.%20The%20alliance%20won%20just%20one%20of%20the%20state's%2039%20seats%20in%202019%20and%20lost%20power%20in%20the%202021%20assembly%20polls.%20Historically%2C%20after%201999%2C%20neither%20Dravidian%20party%20has%20been%20able%20to%20make%20any%20electoral%20impact%20when%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJayalalithaa%20struck%20an%20alliance%20for%20the%202004%20parliamentary%20polls%2C%20but%20it%20was%20routed%2039-0%20by%20the%20DMK-Congress%20combine.%20After%20that%2C%20while%20publicly%20displaying%20proximity%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20she%20avoided%20entering%20into%20a%20formal%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20lesson%20that%20in%20the%20electoral%20math%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20ideologically%20incompatible%20with%20the%20Dravidian%20political%20outlook%2C%20alienated%20a%20core%20section%20of%20Tamil%20polity%20and%20so%2C%20was%20a%20futile%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20learned%20this%20lesson%20in%202001%2C%20when%20it%20lost%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20election%20as%20an%20NDA%20ally.%20While%20the%20party%20clung%20to%20power%20in%20the%20NDA%20till%202004%2C%20it%20shifted%20to%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20before%20the%20parliamentary%20polls%2C%20and%20that%20alliance%20has%20lasted%20to%20date%2C%20despite%20serious%20differences%20and%20a%20brief%20break%20during%20the%202G%20scam%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20history%20is%20by%20way%20of%20reiteration%20that%20the%20AIADMK%20does%20not%20have%20a%20compelling%20electoral%20reason%20to%20remain%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%20It%20had%20stayed%20on%20both%20to%20enjoy%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20Centre%20and%20also%20because%20EPS%20is%20close%20to%20the%20top%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20state%20BJP%20unit%20has%20been%20aggressively%20reiterating%20its%20identity%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20K.%20Annamalai.%20The%20former%20IPS%20officer%20belongs%20to%20the%20same%20OBC%20caste%20as%20that%20of%20E%20Palaniswamy.%20Though%20Annamalai%20lost%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%202021%2C%20he%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20in%20taking%20on%20the%20DMK%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20yatra%20across%20the%20state%20-%20he%20is%20still%20on%20a%20tour%20to%20visit%20all%20234%20assembly%20segments%20which%20the%20AIADMK%20leadership%20has%20not%20joined%20-%20is%20an%20effort%20to%20both%20build%20the%20party%2C%20which%20still%20has%20only%20a%20meagre%20electoral%20presence%2C%20and%20establish%20himself%20as%20a%20personality%20to%20reckon%20with.%20Strong%20personality%20and%20cult%20following%20is%20an%20essential%20trait%20in%20Dravidian%20politics%20and%20EPS%20is%20not%20perceived%20either%20as%20a%20powerful%20orator%20or%20a%20charismatic%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20genuine%20fear%20in%20the%20AIADMK%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%2C%20eventually%2C%20build%20itself%20in%20the%20state%20by%20taking%20over%20the%20AIADMK's%20caste%20vote.%20Given%20that%20the%20DMK%20under%20Stalin%20is%20firmly%20in%20power%20and%20a%20staunch%20Congress%20ally%2C%20it%20is%20obvious%20that%20the%20BJP's%20rise%20in%20vote%20share%20has%20to%20come%20from%20the%20AIADMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20sum%20it%20up%2C%20first%2C%20there%20is%20no%20compelling%20electoral%20reason%20for%20the%20AIADMK%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20alliance%20and%20second%2C%20there%20is%20a%20perceived%20threat%20to%20its%20vote%20from%20its%20own%20ally.%20Even%20these%20two%20reasons%20were%20not%20strong%20enough%20for%20the%20AIADMK%20to%20break%20the%20alliance.%20The%20last%20straw%20was%20a%20hit%20at%20its%20very%20ideological%20and%20emotional%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20sections%20of%20the%20state%20BJP%20leadership%20have%20been%20aggressively%20asserting%20their%20ideological%20beliefs.%20Dravidian%20politics%20is%20built%20on%20foundations%20of%20the%20linguistic%20identity%20born%20out%20of%20the%20anti-Hindi%20agitation%2C%20rationalism%20and%20social%20justice.%20There%20is%20a%20sizeable%20population%20of%20minorities%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Dravidian%20parties%20have%20made%20co-opting%20them%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20their%20identity.%20All%20this%20makes%20an%20aggressive%2C%20ideological%20Hindutva%20reiteration%20unacceptable%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20all%20this%20was%20simmering%2C%20Annamalai's%20reported%20comments%20that%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20DMK%20(Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam)%20CN%20Annadurai%2C%20popularly%20called%20Anna%2C%20%26quot%3Bhad%20mocked%20Hinduism%20in%201956%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20alleged%20comments%20on%20Jayalalithaa%20were%20a%20flash%20point.%20(The%20AIADMK%20split%20from%20the%20DMK%20after%20Anna's%20death%20and%20still%20sees%20him%20as%20its%20guiding%20light)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20first%20para%20of%20the%20AIADMK's%20resolution%20to%20exit%20the%20alliance%20released%20on%20Monday%20mentions%20that%20%26quot%3Bover%20the%20last%20year%20there%20has%20been%20a%20planned%2C%20deliberate%20and%20premeditated%20effort%20to%20misrepresent%20those%20considered%20gods%20of%20our%20movement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20comes%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20confrontation%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20DMK%20scion%20Udayanidhi%20Stalin.%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20ideological%20positions%20of%20the%20AIADMK%20are%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20the%20DMK.%20While%20the%20DMK%20is%20more%20aggressive%20in%20asserting%20it%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20cannot%20dissociate%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20week%20ago%2C%20when%20AIADMK%20leaders%20began%20making%20statements%20of%20breaking%20the%20alliance%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20the%20party%20was%20flexing%20its%20muscles%20at%20a%20time%20when%20seat%20sharing%20negotiations%20were%20on%20with%20the%20BJP.%20There%20were%20reports%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20demanded%20up%20to%2015%20seats%20-%20in%202019%20it%20was%20allotted%20only%20five%20seats%20-%20and%20that%20had%20caused%20a%20rift%20in%20the%20alliance.%20But%20the%20AIADMK's%20statement%20clearly%20indicates%20this%20decision%20is%20not%20a%20mere%20threat%20to%20help%20bargaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20strongly-worded%20resolution%20make%20it%20clear%20the%20party's%20leadership%20feared%20a%20loss%20of%20image%20before%20their%20cadre%20and%20had%20to%20make%20a%20show%20about%20storming%20out.%20Especially%20with%20the%20DMK%20talking%20on%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20could%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20capitulating.%20At%20stake%20was%20not%20just%20the%20image%20of%20the%20party%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20image%20of%20its%20leader%20-%20EPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20very%20difficult%20for%20the%20AIADMK%20to%20walk%20back%20to%20the%20BJP%20after%20such%20a%20strong%20statement%2C%20but%20nothing%20is%20impossible%20in%20politics.%20However%2C%20the%20only%20wiggle%20room%20would%20be%20if%20the%20BJP%20bows%20to%20it%2C%20and%20does%20so%20publicly.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20without%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20even%20begin%20scripting%20a%20Dravidian%20electoral%20story%20in%20the%2039%20parliamentary%20seats%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%201%20in%20Puducherry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(TM%20Veeraraghav%20is%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695706440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F38eggntg_aiadmk-bjp_625x300_19_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Faiadmk-bjp-split-opinion-not-easy-for-bjp-leadership-to-salvage-tamil-nadu-alliance-4423969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20the%20jump%2C%20the%20AIADMK-BJP%20alliance%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20support%20needed%20by%20factions%20of%20the%20Dravidian%20party%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20government%20and%20the%20party%20after%20the%20death%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20J%20Jayalalithaa%20in%202016.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Faiadmk-bjp-split-opinion-not-easy-for-bjp-leadership-to-salvage-tamil-nadu-alliance-4423969%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Faiadmk-bjp-split-opinion-not-easy-for-bjp-leadership-to-salvage-tamil-nadu-alliance-4423969%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Faiadmk-bjp-split-opinion-not-easy-for-bjp-leadership-to-salvage-tamil-nadu-alliance-4423969%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20LIVE%3A%20Metal%20index%20gains%201%25%3B%20Nuvama%20sinks%205%25%2C%20sugar%20stocks%20dip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695706377000%2C%22visu