amp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canada%20Asks%20Citizens%20In%20India%20To%20Stay%20Vigilant%20As%20Row%20Escalates%3A%2010%20Facts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20context%20of%20recent%20developments%20in%20Canada%20and%20in%20India%2C%20there%20are%20calls%20for%20protests%20and%20some%20negative%20sentiment%20towards%20Canada%20on%20social%20media.%20Please%20remain%20vigilant%20and%20exercise%20caution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Canadian%20government%20said%20in%20an%20updated%20advisory.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EKhalistani%20sympathisers%20protested%20outside%20the%20Indian%20embassies%20and%20consulates%20in%20Canada's%20Toronto%2C%20Ottawa%20and%20Vancouver%20today%20over%20Nijjar's%20killing.%20Protesters%20-%20led%20by%20the%20members%20of%20a%20pro-Khalistani%20outfit%20-'Sikhs%20For%20Justice'%20(SFJ)%20-%20were%20seen%20raising%20slogans%20and%20waving%20Khalistani%20flags.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20protests%20come%20a%20week%20after%20Canada%20Prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20kicked%20up%20a%20massive%20diplomatic%20row%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20alleging%20that%20%26quot%3BIndian%20government%20agents%26quot%3B%20could%20be%20behind%20the%20shooting%20of%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ESources%20say%20pro-Khalistani%20extremists%20(PKE)%20have%20started%20openly%20intimidating%20minority%20Hindus%20there%2C%20and%20many%20instances%20of%20defacing%20of%20temples%20have%20been%20reported.%20%26quot%3BThe%20open%20threats%20by%20Khalistanis%20to%20the%20physical%20security%20of%20Indian%20missions%20and%20diplomats%20in%20Canada%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20development%20and%20challenges%20the%20obligation%20of%20Canada%20under%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20government%20officer%20who's%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%C2%A0US%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20Matthew%20Miller%20today%20said%20that%20Washington%20had%20%26quot%3Bpublicly%20and%20privately%26quot%3B%20urged%20India%20to%20cooperate%20in%20the%20Canadian%20probe%20into%20Nijjr%20killing.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20it's%20critical%20that%20Canada's%20investigation%20proceeds%20and%20that%20the%20perpetrators%20be%20brought%20to%20justice.%20And%20we%20have%20publicly%20-%20and%20privately%20-%20urged%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20cooperate%20in%20the%20Canadian%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIndia%20has%20rejected%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegation%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B.%20Canada%20has%20shared%20no%20specific%20information%20regarding%20its%20charges%2C%20India%20said%2C%20flagging%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20condoned%20hate%20crimes%20and%20criminal%20violence%26quot%3B%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIndia%20has%20also%20accused%20Canada%20of%20not%20acting%20upon%20%26quot%3Bspecific%20evidence%20about%20criminal%20activities%26quot%3B%20done%20by%20Canada-based%20individuals.%20The%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20has%20prepared%20a%20list%20of%2019%20fugitive%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20living%20in%20UK%2C%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20Dubai%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20other%20countries%20whose%20properties%20are%20also%20likely%20be%20confiscated%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EJustin%20Trudeau%20also%20claimed%20that%20such%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20allegations%26quot%3B%20were%20shared%20with%20India%20weeks%20ago.%20%26quot%3BCanada%20has%20shared%20the%20credible%20allegations%20that%20I%20talked%20about%20on%20Monday%20with%20India.%20We%20did%20that%20many%20weeks%20ago.%20We%20are%20there%20to%20work%20constructively%20with%20India.%20We%20hope%20that%20they%20engage%20with%20us%20so%20that%20we%20can%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%20very%20serious%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20a%20news%20conference%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ETop%20US%20diplomat%20David%20Cohen%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bshar