%20against%20proving%20his%20credentials%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20on%20a%20show%20with%20the%20ball%20as%20India%20took%20on%20Australia%20in%20the%202nd%20ODI%20of%20the%203-match%20series.%20The%20marquee%20spinner%2C%20who%20hasn't%20been%20in%20India's%20scheme%20of%20things%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%20for%20long%2C%20made%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20selection%20with%20his%20performance%20against%20the%20mighty%20Aussies.%20As%20Ashwin%20claimed%20three%20wickets%20in%20the%20Indore%20match%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20shatter%20an%20all-time%20record%20that%20was%20held%20by%20the%20legendary%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Anil%20Kumble%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F265-anil-kumble-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAnil%20Kumble%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20figures%20of%203%20for%2041%20against%20Australia%2C%20Ashwin%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20India's%2099-run%20victory%20(DLS).%20With%20these%20three%20wickets%2C%20Ashwin%20went%20to%20144%20scalps%20against%20Australia%20in%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20record%20was%20earlier%20held%20by%20Kumble%20who%20has%20142%20wickets%20against%20the%20Aussies.%20Now%2C%20Ashwin%20has%20the%20most%20wickets%20for%20an%20Indian%20against%20a%20single%20opponent%20in%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20duo%20are%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kapil%20Dev%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40958-ramlal-nikhanj-kapil-dev-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E%20(141%20vs%20Pakistan)%2C%20Kumble%20(135%20vs%20Pakistan)%2C%20and%20Kapil%20(132%20vs%20West%20Indies).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ashwin%20would%20hope%20to%20see%20such%20performances%20of%20his%20earn%20him%20a%20spot%20in%20India's%20World%20Cup%20squad%2C%20former%20Australia%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aaron%20Finch%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1011-aaron-finch-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAaron%20Finch%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20think%20that%20would%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20depends%20on%20how%20they%20think%20the%20surfaces%20are%20going%20to%20play%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20and%20by%20that%20time%2C%20I%20think%20the%20skill%20in%20picking%20a%20squad%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20is%20you%20have%20to%20think%20of%20the%20back%20end.%20But%20you%20can't%20think%20too%20much%20about%20it%20because%20you%20have%20to%20get%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Finch%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20might%20struggle%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%2015%2C%20but%20as%20somebody%20who%20has%20played%20so%20much%20cricket%2C%20I%20think%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20group%20that%20is%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%20for%20this%20current%20series%20against%20Australia%2C%20they%20could%20learn%20so%20much%20about%20big%20game%20play.%20Because%C2%A0Ashwin%C2%A0is%20somebody%20that%20stands%20up%20in%20big%20games%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20test%20match%20or%20a%20T20%20game%2C%20he%20has%20done%20it%20all%20throughout%20his%20career.%20So%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20he's%20there%20at%20the%20moment%20as%20a%20mentor%20around%20the%20group%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20him%20making%20that%20last%2015%2C%20unfortunately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Axar%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20injured%2C%20Ashwin%20could%20find%20a%20spot%20in%20India's%2015-man%20squad%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695703980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-