ificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20catalogue%20cells%20and%20predict%20how%20they%20act%20when%20diseased.%20The%20data%20could%20be%20used%20to%20make%20groundbreaking%20new%20discoveries%20that%20could%20help%20cure%2C%20prevent%2C%20or%20manage%20all%20diseases%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20century%2C%20the%20foundation%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20creating%20new%20opportunities%20in%20biomedicine%2C%20and%20building%20a%20high-performance%20computing%20cluster%20dedicated%20to%20life%20science%20research%20will%20accelerate%20progress%20on%20important%20scientific%20questions%20about%20how%20our%20cells%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchanzuckerberg.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fczscience-builds-ai-gpu-cluster-predictive-cell-models%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%20%3C%2Fa%3ECZI%20Co-founder%20and%20Co-CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwhatsapp-introduces-channels-what-is-it-and-how-to-create-one-4389184%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeveloping%20digital%20models%20capable%20of%20predicting%20all%20cell%20types%20and%20cell%20states%20from%20the%20genome%20will%20help%20researchers%20better%20understand%20our%20cells%20and%20how%20they%20behave%20in%20health%20and%20disease%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhen-art-begins-with-profit-humans-of-new-yorks-founder-amid-humans-of-bombay-row-4423748%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Art%20Begins%20With%20Profit...%26quot%3B%3A%20Humans%20Of%20New%20York's%20Founder%20Amid%20Humans%20Of%20Bombay%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20press%20note%2C%20CZI's%20aim%20is%20to%20give%20researchers%20access%20to%20generative%20AI%20to%20study%20healthy%20and%20diseased%20cells.%20Using%20predictive%20models%20of%20human%20cells%20can%20help%20researchers%20better%20understand%20how%20the%20