20Australia%20in%20the%202019%20World%20Cup.%20I%20follow%20both%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli.%20They%20are%20the%20current%20greats%20of%20the%20game.%20Then%2C%20there%20is%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20and%20Jaspreet%20Bumrah.%20Bumrah%20was%20extraordinary%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%202019%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20Yu%20told%20when%20PTI%20caught%20up%20with%20him%20after%20the%20gold%20medal%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20did%20he%20learn%20about%20cricket%3F%20%26quot%3BCricket%20lessons%20are%20given%20in%20my%20university%20in%20Beijing.%20So%2C%20I%20know%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Yu%20gave%20some%20interesting%20insight%20about%20the%20cricket%20arena%20for%20the%20Games%2C%20which%20was%20actually%20a%20flower%20garden%20only%20some%20time%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20not%20much%20cricket%20in%20China%2C%20very%20few%20cricket%20venues%2C%20very%20few%20people%20play%20it%20and%20many%20even%20don't%20know%20how%20it%20is%20played.%20Only%20Guangzhou%2C%20where%20cricket%20was%20played%20during%20the%202010%20Asian%20Games%20has%20a%20permanent%20cricket%20stadium.%20It's%20because%20of%20historical%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYu%20was%20one%20among%20the%20motley%20crowd%20who%20turned%20up%20at%20the%20Pingfeng%20cricket%20field%20at%20the%20Zhejiang%20University%20of%20Technology%20campus%20here.%20The%20venue%20is%20not%20a%20proper%20cricket%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20play%20cricket%20even%20if%20I%20want%20to.%20There%20is%20no%20proper%20ground%20also.%20Even%20this%20ground%20was%20a%20flower%20field%20before%20the%20Asian%20Games.%20It%20was%20converted%20into%20a%20cricket%20field%20for%20the%20Asian%20Games.%20A%20few%20warm-up%20games%20were%20played%20here%20before%20the%20Asian%20Games%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20revers%20Tendulkar%2C%20Yu's%20favourite%20cricketer%20is%20a%20New%20Zealander.%20%26quot%3BMy%20favourite%20is%20Kane%20Williamson%20but%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20is%20a%20legend%20of%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Yu%2C%20who%20is%20doing%20his%20Masters%20Zoology%20in%20a%20University%20in%20Bejing%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20Yu%20is%20not%20going%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20Indian%20men's%20team%20to%20play%20in%20the%20Asian%20Games%20when%20the%20competition%20begins%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spent%201000%20Yuan%20(INR%2011%2C400)%20to%20come%20here%20from%20Beijing.%20I%20have%20my%20studies%20and%20so%20I%20can't%20stay%20back%20for%20the%20men's%20tournament.%20I%20am%20returning%20to%20Beijing%20on%20Tuesday%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20of%20the%20Indians%20were%20also%20among%20the%20crowd%2C%20waving%20the%20national%20flag%20and%20cheering%20the%20Indian%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%2C%20Navneet%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Delhi%20but%20currently%20residing%20in%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Hangzhou%2C%20had%20turned%20up%20with%20his%20friends%20to%20watch%20a%20cricket%20match%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20here%20for%20the%20past%20one%20and%20half%20years%2C%20I%20am%20doing%20business%20in%20fabrics.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20we%20have%20watched%20a%20cricket%20match%20in%20China.%20Cricket%20is%20not%20played%20here%20in%20China%20but%20we%20watched%20cricket%20on%20Indian%20channels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20club%20called%20Hangzhou%20Cricket%20Club.%20We%20do%20practice%20every%20Sunday%20and%20even%20take%20part%20in%20tournaments%20in%20Hangzhou%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Shanghai.%26quot%3B%20Another%20Indian%20Manoj%2C%20hailing%20from%20Mumbai%20but%20now%20settled%20here%20with%20family%20since%202003%2C%20has%20a%20textile%20export%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChinese%20people%20don't%20play%20cricket%20but%20you%20never%20know%20after%20the%20Asian%20Games%2C%20some%20of%20them%20may%20start%20doing%20that.%20We%20(Indians)%20have%20clubs%20here%20and%20we%20sometimes%20play%20inter-city%20tournaments.%20There%20is%20always%20a%20tournament%20in%20Shanghai.%20It%20was%20stopped%20due%20to%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20has%20not%20started%20yet%20after%20that.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20there%20is%20no%20cricket-specific%20stadium%20in%20Hangzhou%2C%20except%20for%20this%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20travel%20to%20Shaoxing%20which%20is%2070%20km%20from%20here%20and%20play%20there.%20But%20that%20is%20also%20a%20football%20stadium.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695698820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F8neg5o5g_smriti-mandhana-twitter_625x300_26_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fchinese-fan-travels-from-beijing-to-watch-mandhana-the-goddess-play-story-is-viral-4422786%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20all%20happened%20when%20the%20fan%20deep-dived%20into%20YouTube's%20treasure%20of%20cricket%20videos%20and%20immediately%20got%20hooked%20to%20artistry%20of%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Mandhana%2C%20three%20of%20his%20favourites.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fchinese-fan-travels-from-beijing-to-watch-mandhana-the-goddess-play-story-is-viral-4422786%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fchinese-fan-travels-from-beijing-to-watch-mandhana-the-goddess-play-story-is-viral-4422786%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fchinese-fan-travels-fr