20statements%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98Prickly%20Nationalism%E2%80%99%3A%20From%20a%20G20%20High%20to%20a%20Post-Canada%20Low%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fglobal-press-views-on-india-canada-row-nijjar-allegations%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Prickly%20Nationalism%E2%80%99%3A%20From%20a%20G20%20High%20to%20a%20Post-Canada%20Low%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20it%20had%20been%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20relief%20in%20India%20that%20there%20was%20muted%20support%20from%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allies%2C%20largely%20based%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.li%2FZmRbZ%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20article%20had%20claimed%20that%20there%20had%20been%20pushback%20from%20the%20other%20members%20of%20Five%20Eyes%20intelligence%20sharing%20network%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20on%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20to%20issue%20a%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Ottawa%20started%20to%20face%20criticism%20that%20it%20was%20all%20alone%20diplomatically%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EWaPo%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20was%20strenuously%20denied%20multiple%20times%20by%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-killing-us-canada-no-special-exemption%5C%22%3Eincluding%20at%20the%20level%20of%20US%20national%20security%20adviser%20Jake%20Sullivan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20weekend%20was%20capped%20with%20the%20US%20ambassador%20to%20Canada%20David%20Cohen%20confirming%20that%20intelligence%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fshared-intelligence-of-five-eye-partners-informed-trudeaus-allegations-says-us-envoy-to-canada%5C%22%3EFive%20Eyes%20countries%20had%20informed%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20all%20the%20foreign%20ministers%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20countries%2C%20one%20by%20one%2C%20had%20made%20public%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3