%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20political%20heads%20of%20the%20foreign%20ministries%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20countries%20made%20public%20statements%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20such%20declarations%20from%20the%20Indian%20foreign%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20or%20any%20other%20political%20figure%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20bit%20unusual%20as%20Jaishankar%20has%20usually%20robustly%20defended%20the%20Indian%20government%20against%20criticism%20from%20foreign%20quarters%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wionews.com%2Fworld%2Fthey-think-its-god-given-right-jaishankar-slams-west-for-commenting-on-rahul-gandhis-disqualification-578344%5C%22%3EGerman%20foreign%20office%20spokesperson%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-us-human-rights-jaishankar%5C%22%3EUS%20secretary%20of%20state%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20words%20criticising%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fexplained-what-jaishankar-said-about-europe-why-germany-chancellor-praises-him-news-263632%5C%22%3EEuropean%20mindset%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Russian%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20had%20caused%20a%20social%20media%20sensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20Jaishankar%20who%20had%20led%20the%20charge%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaking-absurd-claims-does-not-make-others-territory-yours-s-jaishankar-on-china-4339360%5C%22%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20new%20political%20map%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August%20that%20continued%20to%20show%20Aksai%20Chin%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20as%20Chinese%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20special%20session%2C%20the%20foreign%20minister%20left%20for%20New%20York%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly.%20He%20met%20several%20of%20his%20counterparts%20and%20took