%3Cp%3EBetween%20100%2C000%20and%20250%2C000%20women%20were%20raped%20over%20three%20months%20in%201994%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20At%20least%20200%2C000%20women%20were%20raped%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo%20since%201998%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20more%20during%20wars%20in%20Sierra%20Leone%2C%20Liberia%2C%20and%20the%20former%20Yugoslavia%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20it%20is%20also%20used%20to%20deliberately%20infect%20women%20with%20HIV%20or%20render%20women%20from%20the%20targeted%20community%20incapable%20of%20bearing%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20the%202014%20report%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20international%20law%20provides%20protections%20against%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%2C%20enforcement%20of%20the%20provisions%20is%20weak%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkglobalhealth.org%2Farticle%2Fdevastating-use-sexual-violence-weapon-war%5C%22%3ECouncil%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20nonpartisan%20think%20tank.%20The%20International%20Crime%20Court%20has%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20alleged%20war%20crimes%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20though%20legal%20action%20is%20unlikely%20to%20come%20for%20many%20years%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20comes%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInternational%20law%20is%20largely%20ineffective%20at%20preventing%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%20in%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20which%20advocates%20for%20a%20pragmatic%20approach%20to%20helping%20survivors%2C%20rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20the%20near-impossible%20task%20of%20ending%20sexual%20violence%20during%20wartime.%20%26quot%3BSurvivor-centered%20training%20and%20aid%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20support%20victims%20of%20sexual%20violence%20and%20to%20help%20them%20cope%20with%20the%20trauma%2C%20stigma%2C%20and%20the%20health%20consequences%20stemming%20from%20conflict-relat