Illinois%20attorney%20general.%3Cp%3EIllinois%20attorney%20general's%20office%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20building's%20management%2C%20401%20N.%20Wabash%20Venture%20%E2%80%93%20an%20LLC%20owned%20by%20the%20Trump%20Organization%2C%20in%20turn%20owned%20by%20Trump%20%E2%80%93%20is%20now%20backing%20off%20the%20accuracy%20of%20a%20decade's%20worth%20of%20math.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETower%20management%20has%20retained%20two%20engineering%20firms%20to%20do%20a%20%26quot%3Blengthy%26quot%3B%20audit%20of%20its%20monthly%20reporting%2C%20Trump's%20lawyers%20told%20the%20state%20EPA%20in%20an%20August%2014%20letter%20included%20with%20the%20AG's%20latest%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B401%20is%20not%20yet%20able%2C%20as%20of%20today%2C%20to%20confirm%20the%20accuracy%20of%20past%20reports%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20excerpt%20from%20an%20August%2014%2C%202023%20letter%20from%20Trump%20engineers%20addressing%20the%20Illinois%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency's%20concerns%20that%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20%26amp%3B%20Tower%20has%20miscalculated%20a%20decade's%20worth%20of%20data%20on%20its%20intake%20and%20discharge%20of%20Chicago%20River%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650cbb8919f33e0019045eec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22230%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20excerpt%20from%20a%20letter%20from%20Trump%20engineers%20addressing%20the%20Illinois%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency's%20concerns%20that%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20%26amp%3B%20Tower%20has%20miscalculated%20a%20decade's%20worth%20of%20data%20on%20its%20intake%20and%20discharge%20of%20Chicago%20River%20water.%3Cp%3EIllinois%20Attorney%20General's%20Office%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Illinois%20EPA%20responded%20to%20the%20apparent%20discrepancy%20by%20issuing%20Trump%20Tower%20a%20violation%20notice%20on%20August%2031.%20The%20notice%20cites%20the%20tower's%20%26quot%3Bfailure%20to%20comply%20with%20monitoring%2C%20sampling%2C%20and%20reporting%20requirements%26quot%3B%20from%20February%202013%20until%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20read%20their%20own%20meter%2C%26quot%3B%20Albert%20Ettinger%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20the%20Sierra%20Club%20and%20Friends%20of%20the%20Chicago%20River%2C%20told%20Insider.%20The%20two%20groups%20are%20parties%20to%20the%20state's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23962859-trump-tower-chicago-effluence-original-ilag-compliant-130818%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eongoing%2C%202018%20environmental%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20tower%2C%20Trump's%20tallest%20building%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20pattern%20of%20regulation%20defiance%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EState%20Attorney%20General%20Kwame%20Raoul's%20latest%20filing%20seeks%20to%20update%20the%20lawsuit%20to%20reflect%20what%20they're%20calling%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20underreporting%20of%20Chicago%20River%20use%3B%20a%20hearing%20on%20that%20request%20is%20set%20for%20Tuesday%20in%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discrepancy%20is%20just%20the%20latest%20example%20in%20a%20long%20history%20of%20flouting%20state%20and%20federal%20environmental%20regulations%2C%20Illinois%20officials%20allege%20in%20their%20lawsuit%20and%20five%20years%20of%20subsequent%20court%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20Tower%20is%20one%20of%20a%20dozen%20riverfront%20properties%20in%20Chicago%20to%20use%20an%20antiquated%2C%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bonce-through%26quot%3B%20water-intake%20system.%20It%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20circulate%2021.6%20million%20gallons%20of%20river%20water%20through%20its%20building%20each%20day%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%20high-rise%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20construction%20began%20in%202005%2C%20on%20the%20site%20of%20the%20old%20Chicago%20Sun-Times%20plant%2C%20the%20tower%20never%20applied%20for%20the%20required%20permit%20to%20run%20the%20system%2C%20officials%20say.%20It's%20called%20a%20National%20Pollutant%20Discharge%20Elimination%20System%20permit%2C%20as%20heated%20water%20is%20considered%20a%20pollutant%20under%20the%20federal%20Clean%20Water%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20building%20continued%20to%20run%20its%20system%20for%20the%20next%20eight%20years%20as%20if%20no%20oversight%20whatsoever%20was%20required%2C%20operating%20with%20no%20permit%2C%20no%20environmental%20impact%20study%2C%20inadequate%20screening%20and%20no%20monthly%20reporting%20of%20flow%20data%2C%20officials%20allege.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222198%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20laughs%20with%20his%20children%2C%20Ivanka%20Trump%20and%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Jr.%2C%20at%20a%202006%20press%20conference%20for%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20%26amp%3B%20Tower%2C%20which%20would%20open%20in%202009..%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650c8cf612dc4f001a17970e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221644%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump%20Organization%20lawyers%20have%20resisted%20changing%20how%20Trump's%20Chicago%20tower%20heats%20and%20cools.%3Cp%3ECharles%20Rex%20Arbogast%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%3ENot%20the%20first%20time%20their%20math%20has%20been%20in%20question%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20didn't%20apply%20for%20a%20permit%20at%20all%26quot%3B%20said%20Ettinger.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20wasn't%20until%202012%20that%20they%20got%20caught.%26quot%3B%20Trump%20was%20fined%20%2446%2C000%20for%20the%20offense.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20tower%20finally%20got%20its%20NPDES%20permit%20and%20began%20reporting%20that%20it%20was%20discharging%20only%20around%2013%2C600%20gallons%20of%20heated%20water%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20a%20year%2C%20though%2C%20tower%20officials%20admitted%20they%20were%20misplacing%20a%20not-insignificant%20decimal%20point.%20They%20were%20reporting%20every%201%2C000%20gallons%20of%20river-water%20discharge%20to%20the%20state%20as%20if%20it%20were%20a%20single%20gallon%2C%20state%20officials%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20math%20is%20their%20strong%20suit%2C%26quot%3B%20quipped%20Ettinger%2C%20who%20said%20the%20Sierra%20Club%20and%20Friends%20of%20Chicago%20River%20are%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20filing%20their%20own%20joint%20lawsuit%20against%20Trump%20Tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20looked%20at%20their%20meter%20and%20thought%20each%20blip%20on%20the%20meter%20was%20a%20gallon%20and%20instead%20it%20was%201%2C000%20gallons%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222213%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Chicago%20skyline%20at%20night%2C%20showing%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20%26amp%3B%20Tower.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65119c3059fd710019eff80c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221660%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Chicago%20skyline%20at%20night%2C%20showing%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20%26amp%3B%20Tower.%3Cp%3EAP%2FNam%20Y.%20Huh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20Tower%20fixed%20its%20decimal-point%20problem%20and%20in%202014%20began%20operating%20under%20a%20revised%20permit.%20But%20in%20July%2C%202018%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chicagotribune.com%2Fnews%2Fbreaking%2Fct-met-trump-tower-fish-kill-20180618-story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Chicago%20Tribune%20revealed%20ongoing%20alleged%20violations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20failure%20to%20ever%20do%20an%20environmental%20impact%20study%20or%20document%20what%20they%20were%20doing%20to%20prevent%20fish%2C%20invertebrates%2C%20larvae%20and%20eggs%20from%20being%20pulling%20into%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attorney%20general's%20lawsuit%20was%20filed%20the%20next%20month.%20It%20seeks%20fines%20that%20could%20total%20%2412%20million%2C%20money%20which%20Trump%2C%20and%20not%20his%20insurers%2C%20would%20be%20directly%20responsible%20for%20paying%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Filcourtsaudio.blob.core.windows.net%2Fantilles-resources%2Fresources%2Fc5fb1f0e-ce43-4170-8770-eeca91a9d757%2FContinental%2520Casualty%2520Co.%2520v.%2520401%2520North%2520Wabash%2520Venture%2C%2520LLC%2C%25202023%2520IL%2520App%2520(1st)%2520221625.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20appellate%20decision%20found.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20lawsuit%20also%20demands%20that%20Trump%20immediately%20improve%20the%20cooling%20system%20so%20that%20it%20is%20less%20deadly%20to%20aquatic%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20them%20doing%20what%20every%20other%20responsible%20building%20on%20the%20river%20is%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Illinois%20Sierra%20Club%20director%20Jack%20Darin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20installing%20a%20cylinder%20of%20screening%20around%20each%20of%20the%20tower's%20two%20giant%20intake%20pipes%2C%20to%20minimize%20the%20fish%20and%20invertebrate%20life%20being%20trapped%20against%20the%20pipes'%20grating%20or%20sucked%20into%20the%20building%2C%20Darin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222402%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20outside%20Chicago's%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20%26amp%3B%20Tower%2C%20as%20it%20was%20under%20construction%20in%202007.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511a85759fd710019effb08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221801%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20outside%20Chicago's%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20%26amp%3B%20Tower%2C%20as%20it%20was%20under%20construction.%3Cp%3ECharles%20Rex%20Arbogast%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20countered%20in%20court%20filings%20that%20the%20building%20is%20invested%20in%20the%20health%20of%20the%20river%2C%20and%20has%20been%20complying%20with%20all%20reporting%20and%20monitoring%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20actively%20working%20with%20IEPA%20to%20renew%20our%20permit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alan%20Garten%2C%20the%20Trump%20Organization's%20executive%20vice%20president%20and%20chief%20legal%20officer.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20process%20is%20ongoing%20we%20are%20confident%20that%20our%20building%20systems%20fully%20comply%20with%20all%20applicable%20regulations%20and%20there%20is%20no%20environmental%20harm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20rejects%20the%20state's%20demand%20that%20he%20surround%20his%20two%20intake%20pipes%20with%20the%20cylindrical%20screens%20that%20are%20standard%20for%20these%20water-intake%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bwedge%20wire%26quot%3B%20used%20in%20this%20screening%20is%20fine%20enough%20to%20sieve%20out%20almost%20all%20small%20invertebrates%2C%20larvae%2C%20and%20eggs.%20The%20setup%20would%20include%20blasts%20of%20air%2C%20at%20intervals%2C%20that%20clean%20the%20screens%20and%20free%20larger%20fish%20trapped%20against%20them.%20It%20would%20cost%20Trump%20between%20%241.5%20million%20and%20%242%20million%20to%20install.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20in%20his%20own%20court%20filings%2C%20has%20protested%20that%20the%20cost%20is%20prohibitive%2C%20that%20the%20loss%20of%20aquatic%20life%2C%20as%20is%2C%20is%20minimal%2C%20and%20that%20he%20is%20grandfathered%20out%20of%20any%20special%20screening%20requirement%20because%20he%20incorporated%20the%20Sun-Times'%20old%20intake%20piping%20into%20his%20far%20larger%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%2C%20at%20least%2C%20are%20his%20main%20challenges.%20His%20experts%20have%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20bursts%20of%20air%20could%20capsize%20small%20boats%2C%20something%20state%20experts%20say%20could%20be%20averted%20by%20posting%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20like%20standard%20practice%20for%20operating%20a%20skyscraper%2C%26quot%3B%20Darin%20said%20of%20the%20screening%20and%20accurate%20monitoring%20the%20state%20is%20asking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20Trump%20International's%20failure%20to%20do%20it%20is%20just%20an%20example%20of%20their%20apparent%20disregard%20for%20the%20environment%20and%20their%20responsibility%20to%20operate%20the%20building%20in%20a%20lawful%20manner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20impact%20on%20the%20river%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%202018%20lawsuit%2C%20a%20state%20court%20quickly%20ordered%20that%20the%20tower%20undertake%20the%20environmental%20study%20that%20should%20have%20happened%20a%20decade%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20findings%2C%20Trump's%20experts%20estimated%20that%20323%2C000%20individual%20fish%2C%20fish%20eggs%20and%20larvae%20were%20%26quot%3Bimpinged%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20drawn%20into%2C%20the%20tower's%20water-intake%20system%20in%20all%20of%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20number%2C%20while%20%26quot%3Bappreciable%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20based%20on%20insufficient%20sampling%2C%20and%20on%20water-intake%20volumes%20that%20have%20consistently%20been%20underreported%20by%2035%20percent%20%E2%80%93%20that%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bgobbledygook%20math%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20officials%20now%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20they're%20doing%20it%20fraudulently%26quot%3B%20Ettinger%2C%20the%20attorney%20for%20the%20Sierra%20Club%20and%20Friends%20of%20the%20Chicago%20River%2C%20says%20of%20Trump%20Tower's%20troubled%20relationship%20with%20state%20regulators%20and%20basic%20arithmetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20think%20legal%20compliance%20is%20not%20a%20big%20part%20of%20their%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3B%20And%20I%20think%20they%20don't%20really%20care%20so%20long%20was%20they%20don't%20get%20caught.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BFrankly%2C%20it's%20gobbledygook%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attorney%20general's%20environmental%20expert%2C%20Peter%20Alan%20Henderson%2C%20has%20studied%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bonce-through%26quot%3B%20cooling%20systems%20like%20Trump%20Tower's%20for%2040%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20state%20detailed%20what%20Henderson%20called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23980926-people-v-trump-tower-chicago-henderson-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20Tower's%20%26quot%3Bunreasonable%26quot%3B%20lapses%20in%20inspecting%20and%20maintaining%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20instance%20Henderson%20noted%2C%20a%20grill%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bintegral%26quot%3B%20to%20keeping%20marine%20life%20out%20of%20Trump's%20system%20fell%20into%20one%20of%20the%20intake%20chambers.%20It%20was%20not%20re-installed%20for%20at%20least%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222261%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20three%20eldest%20children%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Jr.%2C%20Eric%20Trump%2C%20and%20Ivanka%20Trump%2C%20address%20the%20press%20outside%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20%26amp%3B%20Tower%20in%202007.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65119eebe2c0220019ef46cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221696%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20and%20his%20three%20eldest%20children%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Jr.%2C%20Eric%20Trump%2C%20and%20Ivanka%20Trump%2C%20outside%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20%26amp%3B%20Tower%20in%202007.%3Cp%3ECharles%20Rex%20Arbogast%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Henderson%20who%20told%20Trump's%20lawyers%20%26quot%3Bfrankly%2C%20it's%20gobbledygook%26quot%3B%20when%20asked%20what%20he%20thought%20of%20Trump%20Tower%20expert%20Christopher%20Wiggins'%20flow-rate%20math%20%E2%80%93%20a%20calculation%20involving%20%26quot%