20country%20who%20got%20us%20medals%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20and%20they%20were%20in%20Jantar%20Mantar%20but%20the%20perpetrator%20sits%20here%20today%20%E2%80%93%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20who%20has%20not%20been%20brought%20to%20book%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20if%20you%20are%20really%20interested%20in%20taking%20care%20of%20women%20towards%20betterment%20and%20progress%20then%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20take%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Dastidar%E2%80%99s%20party%20colleague%20TMC%20MP%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20also%20asked%20if%20the%20BJP%20is%20serious%20about%20the%20empowerment%20of%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20struggles%20of%20women%20are%20not%20because%20of%20women%20but%20because%20of%20men%20and%20their%20outlook%20of%20women.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20waste%20my%20time%20on%20a%20former%20wrestling%20chief%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20alluding%20to%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20irony%20of%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20presence%20during%20the%20debate%20was%20also%20raised%20by%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20MP%20Harsimrat%20Kaur%20Badal%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-date-set-for-implementation-as-womens-reservation-bill-is-passed-unanimously-by-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edelimitation%20and%20census%20clause%20tied%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20legislation%2C%20Badal%20said%20that%20before%20an%20election%2C%20every%20political%20party%20comes%20to%20woo%20women%20voters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20aren%E2%80%99t%20crimes%20against%20women%20ever%20discussed%20in%20this%20house%3F%20In%20the%20last%20five%20years%20crimes%20against%20women%20have%20increased%2