Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330663%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Major%20Vivek%20Jacob%20took%20early%20retirement%20from%20the%20Army%20and%20started%20CLAW%20Global%20(Conquer%20Land%2C%20Air%2C%20Water)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20social%20impact%20organisation%20that%20is%20helping%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20experience%20adventure%20sports%20like%20scuba%20diving%2C%20sky%20diving%20and%20mountaineering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Toured%20Across%20India%20To%20Learn%20From%20Farmers%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20a%20Retd%20Colonel%20Found%20Passion%20in%20Orchid%20Farming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EColonel%20Sujan%20Mohanty%20(57)%2C%20is%20a%20retired%20army%20man%20who%20set%20out%20to%20create%20a%20successful%20life%20for%20himself%20post%20his%20service%20of%2022%20years.%20A%20civil%20engineer%20as%20well%2C%20he%20now%20cultivates%20and%20manages%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296147%2Fhow-to-grow-orchids-at-home-delhi-gardener-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorchid%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20living.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENamed%20%E2%80%98Orchid%20n%20More%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20farm%20is%20located%20in%20Kantapada%20village%20near%20Chandaka%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%2C%20about%2023%20km%20from%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20Monalisa%20Mohanty%20(53)%2C%20his%20outfit%20has%20gained%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20about%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%20a%20feat%20which%20they%20managed%20to%20achieve%20in%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F240644%2Findia-orchid-how-to-grow-business-flower-cultivation-import-industrialist-horticulture-department-telangana-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorchid%20cultivation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20feat%2C%20Sujan%20shares%20what%20qualities%20are%20required%20to%20make%20this%20a%20fruitful%20vocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20should%20have%20patience%20and%20perseverance%20to%20take%20up%20this%20task.%20One%20has%20to%20wait%20for%20two%20years%20for%20a%20suitable%20and%20proper%20yield%20at%20first.%20An%20acre%20of%20land%20may%20only%20produce%2060%2C000%20flowers%2C%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20but%20wait%20and%20watch%20in%20wonder%20how%20that%20number%20slowly%20shoots%20up%20to%20almost%20two%20lakhs%20soon.%20My%20training%20in%20the%20army%20has%20helped%20me%20immensely%20with%20this%20profession.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20reason%20why%20I%20am%20now%20able%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20wife%20of%20an%20army%20man%2C%20I%20have%20been%20ingrained%20with%20these%20traits%20as%20well.%20I%20have%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20robust%20support%20system%20both%20in%20his%20personal%20and%20professional%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Monalisa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20smooth%20sailing%20for%20Sujan%20before%20he%20decided%20on%20orchid%20cultivation%2C%20a%20venture%20which%20is%20totally%20alien%20to%20him.%20But%20with%20pure%20dedication%20and%20determination%2C%20his%20idea%20took%20root%20and%20then%20there%20was%20no%20turning%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mohantys%20with%20visitors%20at%20their%20farm.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Moh