menus%20and%20set%20up%20a%20restaurant%20business.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20I%20had%20developed%20a%20fondness%20for%20the%20cuisine%20of%20Kerala.%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20my%20own%20food%20business%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202019%2C%20Margaret%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20started%20a%20street%20food%20stall%20to%20offer%20authentic%20Kerala%20dishes.%20By%20then%2C%20Vinod%20had%20also%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20joined%20his%20wife%20in%20running%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMargaret%20recalls%20how%20the%20American%20customers%20were%20baffled%20at%20first%20when%20she%20started%20selling%20%3Cem%3Eappams%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20often%20asked%20what%20I%20was%20making%20by%20the%20interested%20customers.%20%3Cem%3EAppams%3C%2Fem%3E%20look%20like%20pancakes%20but%20are%20cooked%20on%20only%20one%20side.%20It%20piqued%20their%20interests%20as%20they%20watched%20me%20cook%20it%20and%20wondered%20how%20they%20were%20supposed%20to%20eat%20it.%20I%20would%20tell%20them%20that%20this%20particular%20pancake%20had%20to%20be%20dipped%20in%20a%20curry%20to%20be%20eaten%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20jokingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FThattu-3-1695302832.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2C%20Margaret%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20started%20a%20street%20food%20stall%20to%20offer%20authentic%20Kerala%20dishes.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FThattu-3-1695302832.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FThattu-3-1695302832-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FThattu-3-1695302832-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FThattu-3-1695302832-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FThattu-3-1695302832-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330512%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202019%2C%20Margaret%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20started%20a%20street%20food%20stall%20to%20offer%20authentic%20Kerala%20dishes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20customers%E2%80%99%20curiosity%20and%20being%20open%20to%20what%20we%20offered%20really%20helped%20us%20expand%20our%20client%20base.%20Later%20on%2C%20we%20introduced%20several%20other%20Kerala%20cuisines%20to%20the%20menu%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENearly%2010%20months%20later%2C%20the%20couple%20set%20up%20the%20restaurant%20in%20the%20Chicago%20neighbourhood%2C%20Avondale.%20Today%2C%20they%20serve%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fbeyond-the-sumptuous-sadhya-what-do-ten-days-of-onam-mean-look-like%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKerala%20cuisines%20%3C%2Fa%3Elike%20pork%20chop%3Cem%3E%20peralan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emalabar%20chicken%20biryani%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Echorum%20kariyum%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Kerala%20fried%20chicken%20bites%2C%20and%20eggplant%3Cem%3E%20theeyal%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eother%20than%20the%20weekend%20special%20Onam%20%3Cem%3Esadhya%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%20%3C%2Fem%3Efeatured%20Thattu%20among%20the%20top%2050%20favourite%20restaurants%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20very%20proud%20to%20get%20this%20national%20recognition.%20I%20did%20not%20have%20a%20culinary%20background%20and%20it%20was%20only%20through%20multiple%20visits%20to%20India%20and%20through%20trials%20and%20errors%20that%20I%20learnt%20to%20make%20these%