%3Eshe%20fondly%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20career%20in%20the%20state%20at%20Kaziranga%20as%20a%20probationary%20trainee.%20At%20that%20time%20I%20was%2020%20years%20younger%20and%2020%20kg%20lighter!%20So%20when%20a%20rhino%20chased%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20courage%20and%20strength%20to%20climb%20a%20tree!%20I%20dread%20what%20will%20happen%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20a%20range%20of%20vital%20tasks%2C%20from%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%2C%20to%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20She%20also%20engages%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20delving%20into%20their%20reliance%20on%20the%20forest%20and%20exploring%20avenues%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F215138%2Fsustainable-e-commerce-karnival-shopping-online-eco-friendly-homegrown-products-lifestyle-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Ghosh's%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20Sonali%20Ghosh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20role%20demands%20precise%20monitoring%20of%20wildlife%20through%20scientific%20techniques%20and%20the%20careful%20management%20of%20tourism%20through%20the%20creation%20and%20execution%20of%20ecotourism%20initiatives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20her%20work%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20listener%20and%20understand%20how%20this%20famed%20protected%20area%20works.%20I%20have%20a%20great%20team%20with%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20forest%20frontline-to-area%20ratios%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20priority%20would%20be%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20protection%2C%20ensure%20and%20strengthen%20Rhinoceros%20and%20other%20flagship%20species%E2%80%99%20conservation.%20The%20second%20priority%20would%20be%20the%20utmost%20welfare%20of%20the%20forest%20frontline%20staff%20who%20serve%2024%C3%977%20in%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20conditions%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20has%20only%20been%2020%20days%20since%20Sonali%20assumed%20the%20new%20responsibility%2C%20she%20is%20quite%20geared%20up%20for%20the%20upcoming%20workload.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20great%20responsibility%20and%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20giving%20me%20the%20opportunity.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20wait%20to%20give%20my%20best%20to%20nature%20and%20conserve%20the%20wildlife%20of%20the%20national%20park%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20women%20aspiring%20to%20be%20in%20the%20field%20of%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservation%20in%20India%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20and%20young%20ladies%20who%20love%20outdoors%20and%20want%20to%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20must%20drop%20all%20their%20apprehensions%20and%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20There%20are%20several%20opportunities%20to%20explore%20and%20the%20sky%E2%80%99s%20the%20limit!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695303144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sonali%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20assumed%20the%20role%20as%20the%20field%20director%20of%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20on%201%20September%2C%202023%2C%20grew%20up%20having%20a%20close%20affinity%20to%20animals.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20completed%20her%20graduation%20in%20life%20sciences%2C%20her%20affinity%20had%20turned%20into%20a%20full%20blown%20passion.%20Being%20in%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservation%20for%20decades%2C%20she%20recalls%20the%20hurdles%2C%20challenges%20and%20offers%20a%20glimpse%20into%20her%20life%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tripura%20IAS%20Officer%E2%80%99s%20Idea%20Is%20Preventing%20Girls%20From%20Leaving%20School%3B%20Stopped%2090%20Child%20Marriages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20on%20her%20way%20home%20from%20school%2C%2016-year-old%20Jyotsana%20Akhtar%20from%20Tripura%E2%80%99s%20Amzadnagar%20village%20heard%20people%20whispering%20while%20looking%20at%20her.%20When%20she%20overheard%20their%20conversation%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20aback%20to%20learn%20that%20her%20marriage%20was%20fixed!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20returned%20home%2C%20my%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Emaa%3C%2Fem%3E%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mention%20anything%20about%20the%20marriage.%20I%20found%20out%20from%20the%20villagers%20that%20I%20was%20to%20marry%20a%20man%20twice%20my%20age%20who%20had%20been%20divorced.%20It%20seemed%20like%20all%20my%20fears%20were%20soon%20to%20turn%20into%20reality%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20if%20I%20would%20ever%20return%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jyotsana%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20retaliated%20and%20refused%20to%20get%20married%20so%20early.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20study%20further%20and%20get%20a%20good%20job%2C%20if%20possible%20earn%20better%20than%20the%20man%20with%20whom%20my%20marriage%20was%20fixed.%20But%20my%20parents%20did%20not%20understand%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20week%2C%20she%20approached%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20school%20club%2C%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20teachers%20with%20her%20problem.%20Through%20them%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20intervened%20and%20prevented%20her%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20IAS%20officer%20has%20formed%20158%20school%20clubs%20across%20the%20district%20to%20prevent%20child%20marriages.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330396%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20has%20formed%20158%20school%20clubs%20across%20the%20district%20to%20prevent%20child%20marriages.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20officials%20informed%20my%20parents%20how%20early%20marriage%20would%20affect%20my%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%20and%20also%20told%20them%20that%20child%20marriage%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F108690%2Fchild-marriage-india-chronic-social-evil%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprohibited%20by%20the%20law%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20made%20them%20sign%20an%20affidavit%20promising%20they%20would%20not%20get%20me%20married%20till%20I%20turned%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Jyotsana%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20a%20student%20in%20Class%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20%E2%80%94%20Saju%20Vaheed.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20more%20about%20the%20initiative%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20battle%20against%20child%20marriages%20in%20Tripura%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBeti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20was%20started%20in%202020%20by%20the%20then%20collector%20Debapriya%20Bardhan%20to%20educate%20girls%20on%20adolescence%20and%20reproductive%20health.%20But%20the%20initiative%20turned%20dormant%20as%20schools%20shut%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F257746%2Fias-hero-karnataka-ceo-zilla-parishad-prevents-child-marriage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Saju%20Vaheed%20%E2%80%94%20a%202015%20batch%20IAS%20officer%20from%20Kerala%20%E2%80%94%20took%20over%20and%20joined%20as%20the%20Collector%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20and%20revived%20the%20initiative%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Saju%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20reviving%20this%20project%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20many%20female%20students%20of%20Classes%208%2C%209%2C%20and%2010%20were%20dropping%20out%20of%20school.%20The%20education%20department%20informed%20me%20that%20it%20was%20because%20of%20child%20marriages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20%E2%80%94%20Saju%20Vaheed.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330395%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20IAS%20officer%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20in%20mid-2022%2C%20we%20conducted%20a%20survey%20and%20found%20out%20that%20215%20such%20girls%20got%20married%20in%202020%20and%20the%20number%20was%20209%20in%202021.%20This%20comprised%20over%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20dropout%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20they%20observed%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20girls%20were%20getting%20married%20when%20they%20were%20between%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20means%20that%20girls%20were%20getting%20married%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20were%20entering%20puberty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20were%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years%20in%20Tripura%20%E2%80%94%20the%20third%20highest%20after%20West%20Bengal%20(41.6%20percent)%20and%20Bihar%20(40.8%20percent).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20a%20high%20percentage%20of%20underage%20girls%20are%20getting%20married%20in%20Tripura.%20Another%20issue%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20detect%20ongoing%20child%20marriages%20because%20they%20often%20involve%20local%20cooperation.%20Typically%2C%20we%20only%20find%20out%20about%20the%20marriage%20through%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20boyfriend%2C%20and%20sometimes%20we%E2%80%99re%20notified%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20making%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20prevent%20the%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20departments%20like%20health%20and%20social%20welfare%20would%20only%20get%20to%20know%20about%20these%20marriages%20when%20these%20young%20girls%20got%20pregnant%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20avail%20government%20schemes.%20Even%20though%20the%20departments%20knew%20it%20was%20illegal%20for%20these%20young%20girls%20to%20be%20married%2C%20they%20found%20themselves%20helpless%20when%20they%20found%20out%20about%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20early%20pregnancies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saju%20Vaheed%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20to%20utilise%20Balika%20Manch%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330398%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaju%20Vaheed%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20to%20utilise%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsidering%20it%20his%20duty%20as%20DM%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F62502%2Fchild-marriage-education-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevent%20child%20marriages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20and%20decided%20to%20utilise%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20three-tiered%20approach%20to%20secure%20the%20future%20of%20young%20girls%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20informs%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20club%20of%20school-going%20girls%20from%20Class%206%20to%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20female%20teacher%20is%20appointed%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20club.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20female%20student%20is%20appointed%20as%20the%20convenor%20who%20keeps%20track%20of%20the%20female%20students%E2%80%99%20attendance%20in%20their%20classes.%20If%20a%20girl%20is%20absent%20for%20more%20than%20a%20week%2C%20she%20reports%20about%20it%20to%20the%20chairman.%20On%20learning%20this%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%20%3C%2Fem%3Erepresentatives%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Evisit%20the%20absentee%E2%80%99s%20house%20to%20enquire%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20learn%20that%20the%20family%20is%20forcing%20the%20girl%20to%20get%20married%2C%20they%20try%20to%20convince%20the%20family%20to%20get%20her%20back%20to%20school%20citing%20legal%20complications%20of%20the%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20formed%20WhatsApp%20groups%20of%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%2C%20women%20school%20management%20committees%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Childline%2C%20child%20welfare%20committees%2C%20and%20district-level%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%2C%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%20inform%20the%20group%20members%20about%20the%20case.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20parents%20are%20not%20convinced%2C%20then%20administrative%20support%20is%20sought.%20This%20is%20when%20our%20second%20layer%20of%20officials%20comes%20into%20the%20picture.%20It%20comprises%20a%20one-stop%20centre%20(where%20young%20girls%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20experts%20for%20counselling)%2C%20a%20district%20child%20protection%20unit%2C%20counsellors%2C%20psychologists%2C%20and%20legal%20practitioners%20who%20reach%20out%20to%20families%20to%20convince%20them.%20Most%20of%20the%20cases%20get%20resolved%20in%20the%20second%20layer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Tripura%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20were%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330400%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20Tripura%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20are%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20the%20families%20start%20questioning%20our%20rights%20to%20prevent%20the%20marriage%2C%20we%20activate%20our%20third%20layer.%20My%20sub-divisional%20magistrate%20rushes%20to%20the%20spot%20and%20tells%20the%20parents%20that%20the%20administration%20shall%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family%20as%20child%20marriage%20is%20a%20punishable%20offence.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20if%20families%20go%20ahead%2C%20we%20send%20police%20officers%20to%20their%20homes%20and%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family.%20We%20then%20get%20an%20affidavit%20signed%20by%20the%20parents%20stating%20that%20they%E2%80%99ll%20not%20marry%20off%20their%20daughters%20until%20they%20are%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20timely%20intervention%2C%20Saju%20has%20been%20able%20to%20prevent%2090%20planned%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20district%20in%20the%20past%20year%20with%20the%20help%20of%20158%20school%20clubs%20across%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20if%20we%20are%20able%20to%20continue%20this%20way%20for%20another%20year%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20eradicate%20child%20marriages%20in%20our%20district.%20Seeing%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20work%2C%20the%20state%20government%20aims%20to%20expand%20this%20initiative%20across%20Tripura.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20work%20is%20deeply%20satisfying%20to%20me%20because%20when%20these%20girls%20talk%20to%20me%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20preventing%20marriages%3B%20we%E2%80%99re%20saving%20lives.%20These%20young%20girls%20now%20have%20a%20platform%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns.%20While%20I%E2%80%99m%20involved%20in%20various%20other%20development%20projects%2C%20this%20one%20is%20particularly%20dear%20to%20me.%20I%20believe%20it%20will%20ensure%20a%20better%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tripura%20is%20notorious%20for%20child%20marriages%20with%20four%20in%2010%20girls%20getting%20married%20before%20turning%2018.%20In%20a%20novel%20approach%2C%20South%20Tripura%20District%20Magistrate%20Saju%20Vaheed%20revived%20%E2%80%98Balika%20Manch%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20school%20club%20cum%20platform%20to%20prevent%20young%20girls%20from%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%20and%20getting%20married.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Startup%20Will%20Help%20You%20Find%20Less%20Crowded%20Fuel%20Stations%2C%20For%20CNG%20%26amp%3B%20EVs%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20got%20his%20licence%20at%2018%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20tried%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306067%2Fcollege-dropout-launches-ev-startup-builds-made-in-india-luxury-electric-suv-pravaig%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriving%20a%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20every%20other%20person.%20However%2C%20he%20would%20often%20end%20up%20getting%20into%20accidents%2C%20and%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20other%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20stop%20driving.%20This%20made%20him%20a%20regular%20user%20of%20cab%20services%20like%20Ola%20and%20Uber.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20decision%20to%20stay%20off%20the%20roads%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20startup%20idea%20which%20aimed%20to